('axai_ch08_023', 'For a zero-order reaction, the half-life is proportional to:', 'mcq', '["1/[A]â‚€","[A]â‚€","[A]â‚€آ²","ln[A]â‚€"]', '[A]â‚€', 'medium', 6, 'both', 'For zero order, tâ‚پ/â‚‚ = [A]â‚€/2k, so it is proportional to the initial concentration.', 'chem', 'ch08', 'ch08t1', 'ch08t1s2'),
